Baseball American League

BOSTON RED SOX -- Acquired Sean Ross, outfielder, and Nate Minchey, pitcher, from the Atlanta Braves to complete the trade for Jeff Reardon pitcher. Assigned Ross and Minchey to Pawtucket of the International League. Purchased the contract of Ken Ryan, pitcher, from Pawtucket.

National League

ATLANTA BRAVES -- Designated Mark Davis, pitcher, for assignment.

CINCINNATI REDS -- Placed Greg Swindell, pitcher, on the 15-day disabled list. Recalled Dan Wilson, catcher, from Nashville of the American Association. Optioned Rick Wrona, catcher, to Nashville.